Per our call today we ran the following instant job in both the Test and Prod Environments

 

Netwrix Access Analyzer (NAA) formally Netwrix Enterprise Auditor (NEA) formally StealthAUDIT (SA)

Netwrix Enterprise Auditor vl 1.6 > Administration > Jobs Tree > Instant Job Wizard > FS_MigrateSchema Job

https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Admin/Jobs/InstantJobs/FS_MigrateSchema.htm 

 

 

Recommend the following to help with Slow NEA Console UI issues 

CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [Messages_JobName_JobRunTimeKey_Index] ON [dbo].[SA_Messages]

(

[JobName] ASC,

[JobRunTimeKey] ASC

)

INCLUDE([MSG_TYPE])
